---
import MarketingPageLayout from '@/layouts/marketing_page_layout.astro';
---

<MarketingPageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | kuku"
  description="How kuku collects, uses, and protects your information."
>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="lp-lead">
    Last updated: April 14, 2026. This policy describes how kuku (&ldquo;we,&rdquo;
    &ldquo;us&rdquo;) handles information when you use our website and desktop application.
  </p>
  <div class="lp-prose">
    <p>
      <strong>Who we are.</strong> kuku is operated in connection with the address listed on our website
      footer. For privacy inquiries, contact us through the channels we publish on our site or repository.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Information we collect.</strong> We may collect information you provide (such as account
      or support emails), technical data from the app or site (such as device type, app version, and crash
      logs), and usage data needed to run and improve the product. If you use optional cloud or sign-in
      features, we process the data required to provide those services.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>How we use information.</strong> We use data to provide and maintain kuku, fix bugs, improve
      performance and security, communicate with you about the product, and comply with law. We do not
      sell your personal information.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Storage and retention.</strong> We keep information only as long as needed for the purposes
      above or as required by law. Local data on your device stays under your control unless you choose
      to sync or upload it.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Third parties.</strong> We may use infrastructure or analytics providers that process data
      on our behalf under contracts that limit their use. We may link to third-party sites; their policies
      govern those sites.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Your choices.</strong> Where applicable, you may access, correct, or delete certain account
      information, opt out of non-essential communications, or uninstall the application. Some requests
      may be limited by law or legitimate business needs.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Children.</strong> kuku is not directed at children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect
      their personal information.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>International users.</strong> If you access kuku from outside the United States, your information
      may be processed in the United States or other countries where we or our providers operate.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Changes.</strong> We may update this policy from time to time. We will post the revised
      version on this page and adjust the &ldquo;Last updated&rdquo; date.
    </p>
  </div>
</MarketingPageLayout>
